title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861.
author: Victoria
snippet: In a little more than two hours we were at Loc/i Callater — the road was very bad indeed as we approached the loch, where our ponies were waiting for us.

title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861.
author: Victoria
